              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Targets were irradiated for times of 3-7h with heavy",
                "ion beams ranging in intensity from 10**10-10**12",
                "ions/sec."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "62-SM-154",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.987
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Targets consisting of deposits",
                "of 154Sm20 of various thicknesses ranging from 0.3 to",
                "1.0mg/cm2 on a 4.7mg/cm2 Be backing. In the",
                "differential range measurements, all fragments",
                "recoiling from the target in the forward hemisphere",
                "were stopped in a stack of A1 foils of various",
                "thicknesses (0.25-1.6 mg/cm2)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC",
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Following irradiation, the catcher",
                "foils from the angular distribution measurements were",
                "cut into pieces representing various angular",
                "intervals. These pieces along with the individual",
                "foils from the differential range measurements and",
                "the target foils were assayed by gamma ray",
                "spectroscopy beginning a few minutes after end of",
                "irradiation and continuing for periods of up to 3",
                "months in laboratories at MSU and LBL."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
